<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <title>Welcome to the Hackathon!</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #2196f3;
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #666;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <h1>Welcome to the Hackathon!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class='content'>
        <p>Dear {{userName}},</p>
        <p>Congratulations! You have successfully joined the hackathon "<strong>{{hackathonName}}</strong>".</p>
        <p>We're excited to have you as a participant. Get ready to innovate, collaborate, and showcase your skills!</p>
        <p>You can now submit your project once the hackathon starts. Check our platform for updates and deadlines.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br />The Hackathon Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class='footer'>
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
      </div>
  </body>
</html>